graph.algorithms.connectivity

Class PlanarAugmentationLabel<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.algorithms.connectivity.PlanarAugmentationLabel<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The vertex type
    E - The edge type

    public class PlanarAugmentationLabel<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A bundle of pendants together with its parent is called a label. If parent is a c-vertex, the label is also called c-label, otherwise it is calse a b-label The size of a label is the number of pendants contained by the bundle
    Author:
    Renata
